@startuml UC18_sequence
title UC18 - Admin phan hoi ho tro
actor "Admin" as Admin
boundary "AdminSupportInboxPage" as AdminSupportInboxPage
control "AdminSupportMessageController" as AdminSupportMessageController
control "SupportMessageService" as SupportMessageService
database "UserRepository / users" as UserRepo
database "SupportMessageRepository /\nsupport_messages" as SupportRepo

Admin -> AdminSupportInboxPage : Mo trang Ho tro khach hang
AdminSupportInboxPage -> AdminSupportMessageController : GET /api/admin/messages/conversations
AdminSupportMessageController -> SupportMessageService : getAdminConversations(adminUsername)
SupportMessageService -> UserRepo : findByUsernameIgnoreCase(adminUsername)
SupportMessageService -> SupportRepo : findLatestByCustomerConversation()
SupportMessageService --> AdminSupportMessageController : ConversationSummary[]
AdminSupportMessageController --> AdminSupportInboxPage : Danh sach hoi thoai

Admin -> AdminSupportInboxPage : Chon 1 hoi thoai theo customer
AdminSupportInboxPage -> AdminSupportMessageController : GET /api/admin/messages/conversations/{customerId}?markRead=true
AdminSupportMessageController -> SupportMessageService : getAdminConversation(adminUsername,customerId,markRead)
SupportMessageService -> UserRepo : findByUsernameIgnoreCase(adminUsername)
SupportMessageService -> UserRepo : findById(customerId)
SupportMessageService -> SupportRepo : markCustomerMessagesReadByAdmin(customerId)
SupportMessageService -> SupportRepo : findByCustomerIdOrderByCreatedAtAscIdAsc()
SupportMessageService --> AdminSupportMessageController : SupportConversationResponse
AdminSupportMessageController --> AdminSupportInboxPage : Hien thi lich su chat

Admin -> AdminSupportInboxPage : Nhap noi dung phan hoi
Admin -> AdminSupportInboxPage : Bam nut Gui
AdminSupportInboxPage -> AdminSupportMessageController : POST /api/admin/messages/conversations/{customerId}/reply
AdminSupportMessageController -> SupportMessageService : sendAdminReply(adminUsername,customerId,content)
SupportMessageService -> UserRepo : findByUsernameIgnoreCase(adminUsername)
SupportMessageService -> UserRepo : findById(customerId)
SupportMessageService -> SupportRepo : save(SupportMessage senderRole=ADMIN/SUPER_ADMIN)
SupportRepo --> SupportMessageService : SupportMessage
SupportMessageService --> AdminSupportMessageController : SupportMessageResponse
AdminSupportMessageController --> AdminSupportInboxPage : 201 Created + tin nhan moi
AdminSupportInboxPage --> Admin : Hien thi tin phan hoi

alt Khong du quyen / customer khong ton tai /\nnoi dung rong hoac qua dai
  SupportMessageService --> AdminSupportMessageController : IllegalArgumentException
  AdminSupportMessageController --> AdminSupportInboxPage : 400 + thong bao loi
  AdminSupportInboxPage --> Admin : Hien thi loi
else Loi CSDL
  SupportRepo --> SupportMessageService : DataAccessException
  AdminSupportMessageController --> AdminSupportInboxPage : 500 Loi he thong
  AdminSupportInboxPage --> Admin : Hien thi Loi he thong
end
@enduml
